{"tid":1453974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無一個警察係無辜】試下係機場播呢條811英文字幕片比外國人睇","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:59.000Z","uid":27987,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e093a985c07a3f510820553f3eeb15de37b6d984","tid":1453974,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NOwsydey7b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNOwsydey7b8&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=ab431d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NOwsydey7b8</a><br />\n<br />\n訓唔著又憑怒火剪左條片<br />\n趁今日大家去機場<br />\n如果想播片比外國人睇可以一試 有簡單字幕形容發生左咩事<br />\n又可以send埋比人權組織做證據<br />\n希望幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎大家用community settings加其他語言字幕！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlease share this video around the world.<br />\nWe need the world to see for themselves about the brutal acts of the Hong Kong Police Force.<br />\n<br />\nWhat Happened in Hong Kong - a brief summary of what the Hong Kong Police Force did on 11 August, 2019.<br />\n1. Shooting bean bag bullets directly to a female protester's eye, causing permanent blindness<br />\n2. Brutally beaten up the arrested protesters<br />\n3. Planting fake evidence on protesters (putting sharp bamboo into protester's backpack)<br />\n4. Disguise as demonstrators to take the lead<br />\n5. Shoot tear gas bullets at the protesters right outside MTR subway station at a distance of less than one metre.<br />\n6. Pushing down civilians on the elevators in subway station<br />\n7. Allowing gangsters chsaing up and beating protesters and civilians on the street<br />\n8. Launching tear gas canisters in MTR subway stations at civilians<br />\n9. Launching tear gas canisters outside of the elderly home and nearby residences"},{"pid":"ae7ed8c6eb3bad5b3739667db924731db026a4e8","tid":1453974,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114be60bcd001e754a9668bfc78b39a3380844a3","tid":1453974,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcc344192d345884739f365dc0a4bdad4ee2dca","tid":1453974,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！播片好有用咖"},{"pid":"5fbdf818f51605c85174b3556b45fdf26ebafd9b","tid":1453974,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"播片呀機場"},{"pid":"daa2b7553eda715ea4aba22ac5c32371f1cb337d","tid":1453974,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"推到比機場啲人見到"},{"pid":"884e28f02a32cf3205c9c8358ea4e080d4525307","tid":1453974,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"絕對有用！<br />\n<br />\n公司外國人有時拎返片來問我架會！<br />\n堅有用！"},{"pid":"50ddbd0bd11ec931fc0e7ee3ae557bfb191ae085","tid":1453974,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki